*
!Dockerfile
!maintainpro/
!maintainpro/**

# Re-exclude generated or heavy content inside maintainpro
maintainpro/**/node_modules
maintainpro/**/.next
maintainpro/**/.open-next
maintainpro/**/dist
maintainpro/**/.turbo
maintainpro/**/coverage
maintainpro/**/build
maintainpro/apps/mobile/.dart_tool
maintainpro/apps/mobile/build
maintainpro/**/*.tsbuildinfo
maintainpro/*.log
